channel.title: Two Interfaces at One Time?
channel.description: I am currently running a 508 and wanted to know if its possible to have two interfaces up and one time? For example, I have a timer set up to show up in the bottom right... but when you go into Godwars, you can't see the timer because the Godwars kill count interface (upper right) overrides it... I would like to use both at the same time because they wouldn't clash, and are located at different spot on the screen. Is this possible?
